Package: rsixer
Title: R6-Based Shiny Application Demo
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Martin", "Frigaard", , "mjfrigaard@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application demonstrating R6 object-oriented design patterns
    for building modular, maintainable Shiny apps. Showcases tooltip and
    hover-info handling with financial data from tidyfinance and tidyquant.
